reviewText: Nick is funny as always, I'm happy to pay.
Nick DiPaolo is amazing. Every time. And here he is again, killing it. You won't be disappointed.
This is a hilarious special!!! He is one of the best and quickest comedians working today.  Buy everything!!!
If you are a fan of a clever, quick witted comedian, Nick Dip is for you.
If you like real comedy this is the one dvd you have to get nick dipaolo always hilarious does it again
